    30	
    31	- symptom: the conversation ends with a strong brief but no verified asset -> cause: the prompt/art-direction stage was treated as if it proved execution -> fix: do not call the LP image complete until a rendered file or tool output is present and verified [Task 1]
    32	- symptom: a future agent improvises a generic startup hero -> cause: the unusually specific anti-pattern list is ignored or compressed away -> fix: run a hard-constraint compliance check against the user's exclusion list before finalizing any Smitch visual [Task 1]
